<p><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">BYU-Idaho recommends that students purchase their HP or Apple laptop through the University Store.  Purchases can be made online at byuibookstore.com or on campus.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">The negotiated prices on specific models listed through the University Store are lower than students can obtain by ordering directly through HP or Apple.</span></p>
<p align="justify"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">Special Academic MS Office Suite pricing is also available for both Operating Systems through the University Store.</span></p>
